Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
delete_metric_page(25.10)                            delete_metric_page(25.10)

Name
       delete_metric_page - Deletes a metric page

Syntax
       delete_metric_page

       [-help]

       [-format {html excel text}]

       -name <page_name>

       Deletes a metric page.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

              For a detailed description of the command, use the man command:

              man delete_metric_page

       -format {html excel text}
              Specifies configuration for the report_metric format.

              Data_type: enum, optional

       -name <page_name>
              Specifies the name of the metric page to be deleted.

              Data_type: string, required

       Example
              * The following command creates the metric page, User.

                delete_metric_page -name User

Related Information
              * create_metric_page

